name: BONE SHIBASWAP from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x9813037ee2218799597d83D4a5B6F3b6778218d9. Bone is a governance token of Shibaswap ecosystem which will allow the #ShibArmy to vote on upcoming proposals. The more BONE the user holds, the more weight of their vote carries in these future endeavors.
